snippet.title: Isle Of Birds - Demo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Isle Of Birds Demo! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/3182420/Isle_of_Birds/

Join Our Community! - https://discord.gg/YZ7Y7qVJgE
Buy us a Coffee? 🥹 - https://buymeacoffee.com/shibadogstudios
~~~~~~~~~~
Isle Of Birds is a cozy, bird-placement game co-developed and published by Obfuscate Interactive and Shiba Dog Studios - Coming in full to Steam Q4 2024
~~~~~~~~~~
Software we use: Adobe CC, Logic Pro X, Godot 4.1, Unity 2022 LTS, Godot 4.1, Aseprite, Blender
~~~~~~~~~~
Subscribe for more streams and cozy game dev content - if you enjoyed, leave a like! If not, leave a dislike and tell me why in the comments - Thanks for watching!
